  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "For instance, Keith's (1988) review centered on studies that applied SR to investigate instructors' cognitive processes, which, although valuable at the time, can only provide limited guide for current applications of SR in education.",
    "More recently, Gazdag et al., (2019) reviewed 35 articles on the use of Video Stimulated Recall (VSR) to enhance instructors' reflective thinking.",
    "However, this study's scope was confined to implementing VSR in teacher training and excluded studies in broader educational settings.",
    "Therefore, further studies are needed to comprehensively examine the application of SR across diverse contexts.",
    "The present study offers a comprehensive review of research using SR in manifold teaching and learning contexts over the past decade."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "For instance, Keith's (1988) review centered on studies that applied SR to investigate instructors' cognitive processes, which, although valuable at the time, can only provide limited guide for current applications of SR in education.",
    "More recently, Gazdag et al., (2019) reviewed 35 articles on the use of Video Stimulated Recall (VSR) to enhance instructors' reflective thinking."
  ]
